      "about_company": "<p>DevExpress (Developer Express) is a software development company based in the United States.<br />\nIt produces coding assistance/productivity tools, application frameworks and component libraries for JavaScript (JS/TS), C#/Visual Studio, and Delphi/C++ Builder developers. The major part of its product line is React/Angular/Vue/jQuery, Microsoft .NET WinForms, WPF, .NET MAUI, ASP.NET Core Blazor/MVC/Razor Pages, and VCL components that replicate the UI of Microsoft Windows and Microsoft Office applications. <br />\nDevExpress helps you build applications for Windows, Web, mobile with all of the DevExpress platform controls and more (Enterprise and Server Tools like Reporting, BI Dashboard, Office File APIs, Application Framework and ORM).<br />\nDevExpress has won many industry awards for its products.<br />\nLearn more at <a href=\"https://www.devexpress.com/aboutus/\">https://www.devexpress.com/aboutus/</a>.</p>\n",
